query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('physics')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('astronomy',
'astrophysics',
'electricity',
'electrons',
'everyday-life',
'inertial-frames',
'nuclear-physics',
'orbital-motion',
'potential',
'schroedinger-equation',
'space-expansion',
'standard-model',
'supersymmetry',
'terminology');
